            <p class="text-justify">Turkish Airlines is the largest mainline and national carrier of Turkey. It provides scheduled services to 315 destinations in Europe, Asia, Africa, and America from a single airport than any other airline in the world, and flies to 126 countries, more than any other airline. The airline is known for its frequent flyer program called Miles & Smiles and corporate clubs. </p>
