            <h2>Cancellation policy </h2>
            <p class="text-justify">According to <a href="https://www.faresmatch.com/turkish-airlines-cancellation-policy.aspx">Turkish Airline’s cancellation policy</a>, you can cancel a flight ticket within 24 hours of booking without paying any cancellation fee making sure that the booking was made at least 7 days before the departure date. </p>
            <h3>Refund policy </h3>
            <p class="text-justify">If you cancel the flight ticket within 24 hours of booking, you are eligible for a refund. If the airline cancels your confirmed <a href="https://www.faresmatch.com/">flight ticket </a>or reschedules your flight and this causes you to miss a connecting flight, you qualify to receive a full refund. Also, if your co-passenger or close relatives dies, you may get a full refund after submitting the documents and the airline agreeing to it. </p>
            <h4>Frequently asked question</h4>

            <h3 class="text-justify">How to cancel a flight ticket with Turkish Airlines? </h3>
            <p class="text-justify">You can call the Turkish Airlines customer care office and inform them about the cancellation. You may also contact your kiosk to help you through the cancellation process. Apart from this, you may also visit the official website of the airlines and cancel your flight ticket. </p>
            <h3 class="text-justify">How can I make the request for a refund? By when can I expect it? </h3>
            <p class="text-justify">You can fill out the refund form on the official website of fill out the refund form or call customer care. You can expect a refund from the airlines within seven to ten business days. </p>
            <h3 class="text-justify">Can I ask for compensation if my flight gets delayed by 5 hours? </h3>
            <p class="text-justify">If your replacement flight delays your arrival by 5 or more hours or your flight was canceled less than 14 days before departure, you are eligible to get a full refund. Make sure that you fill out the refund request form. </p>
            <h3 class="text-justify">How to check if my flight is refundable? </h3>
            <p class="text-justify">You can check if your flight is refundable by visiting the official website of the airline and entering the ticket or document number and the Turkish Airlines website will display refund eligibility and information. </p>
